16 SECTION.
17 (e) Except as otherwise provided in this subtitle, the applicant shall pass an
18 examination given by the Commission or the Commission’s designee under this subtitle.
19 (f) (1) If an applicant is not a resident of the State, the applicant shall submit
20 to the Commission an irrevocable consent, as provided under this subsection.
